This R package contains Rust code which depends on the Rust crates listed below.
The source code is vendored in the R package and can also be found at
https://crates.io/crates/XXXX, where XXXX is a crate name.
The authors of these Rust crates are listed below.

Alex Crichton <alex@alexcrichton.com>     : cfg-if, proc-macro2, wit-bindgen
bluss                                     : either, matrixmultiply, rawpointer
Brendan Zabarauskas <bjzaba@yahoo.com.au> : approx
David B. Dahl <dahl@stat.byu.edu>         : dahl-bellnumber, dahl-partition, dahl-salso, rbindings, roxido, roxido_macro
David Tolnay <dtolnay@gmail.com>          : proc-macro2, quote, syn, unicode-ident
Jack Wrenn <jswrenn@amazon.com>           : zerocopy, zerocopy-derive
Jim Turner                                : ndarray
Josh Stone <cuviper@gmail.com>            : autocfg
Joshua Liebow-Feeser <joshlf@google.com>  : zerocopy, zerocopy-derive
R. Janis Goldschmidt                      : matrixmultiply
The CryptoCorrosion Contributors          : ppv-lite86, rand_chacha
The Rand Project Developers               : getrandom, rand, rand_chacha, rand_core, rand_pcg
The Rust Project Developers               : libc, num-bigint, num-complex, num-integer, num-traits, rand, rand_chacha, rand_core
Ulrik Sverdrup "bluss"                    : ndarray
